# ── IDE / OS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~

# ── Credentials and large reference docs ─────────────────────────────
.env
*.pem
*.key

# ── Reference PDFs and .docx notes ───────────────────────────────────
# These are copyrighted research papers / personal notes. They live
# locally so you can read them while editing main.tex, but they should
# not be pushed to a public GitHub repo. Comment any line below if you
# do want a particular file in the repo.
*.pdf
*.docx
!figures/*.pdf

# ── Paper sources and private docs (kept LOCAL only) ─────────────────
# The GitHub repo is intended to host ONLY the code Colab needs to run
# the experiments. Drafts, the paper itself, and internal reports stay
# off GitHub.
main.tex
IMPLEMENTATION_REPORT.md
*.tex
!impl/**/*.tex
NOTES.md
DRAFT*.md

